title: 1.2m RG6 TV Coaxial Cable Connectors Set,F Male to F Male,Aerial TV Cable Extension with Compression Connectors,75 Ohm Coax for Sky,Freesat,Virgin Media,Broadband,Satellite,High-Speed Digital Router
features: Enhanced Signal Quality & Durability – The RG6 coaxial cable ensures a reliable connection for broadband, satellite TV, and digital devices, thanks to nickel-plated brass connectors. This reduces noise and interference, providing clearer picture and sound, making it ideal for high-speed internet, TV, and other multimedia systems.

Versatile Use – Built with double rubber O-rings and waterproof sealing, this coaxial cable is perfect for both indoor and outdoor installations. Its design ensures reliable performance in extreme conditions, making it suitable for long-term outdoor use without compromising signal quality.

Complete Coaxial Kit for Seamless Installation – The set includes a 75ohm RG6 cable with brass compression connectors, a lead-free PVC jacket, and an easy-rotate nut for quick attachment. With the additional extension coupler, you can easily connect multiple cables, ensuring hassle-free installation and reliable signal extension.

Universal Compatibility for Multiple Devices – This coaxial cable supports a wide range of RG6-wired devices such as satellite TV, high-speed internet, digital TV, and more. Its versatile design makes it compatible with most F-type connectors, providing an all-in-one solution for your multimedia setup.

Easy to Install – Satellite cable extension use injection molding to robust joint.it can use in both indoor and outdoor. Consistently and reliably provides you with a high-definition video and audio signal
